{"tid":1267059,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"羅馬唔係一日建成，革命都唔係","createTime":"2019-06-29T17:15:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-29T18:16:41.000Z","uid":40855,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2b7666157d5991b2bff7b3235522f22af675a32c","tid":1267059,"uid":40855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T17:15:15.000Z","msg":"係，係心灰意冷，左右無路，好想搵突破點&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n但古住今來，革命都係長久抗戰，唔好因為一時三刻失敗就氣餒喪志，更加唔好去死。<br />\n我哋一無所有，剩低嘅只有信念，前人種樹，後人乘涼，唔好爭一朝一夕。<br />\n一四年佔領運動輸得好慘烈，但正正係一四年嘅經驗，令到一九年香港人開始明白進退之道，呢個世界所有嘢都互相影響，你睇唔到，唔代表唔會改變。<br />\n蝴蝶效應大家都聽過，唔好輕看曾經嘅付出，幾微小都好，都一定有作用。<br />\n加油呀香港人，千祈千祈唔好死。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1beaa87e5889ecd837f8d806e26c83990821c7da","tid":1267059,"uid":5680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T17:18:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Q-kGIHSHLl0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FQ-kGIHSHLl0&d=FGEw0iwwiNltpS2R1LMyGprbLZzzsfwfKyNyJagnZM4%3D&h=77169f36\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Q-kGIHSHLl0</a>"},{"pid":"9417cde65de3462758239b6f3f892c781b9b4f46","tid":1267059,"uid":54228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T18:16:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J6ogywo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ6ogywo.png&h=a84d61c5&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}